name: Planet BTC
description: BTC ruled the galaxy for years. Its inception paved the way for the development of the crypto galaxies, as its undeniably robust and immutable properties solidified Planet BTC as the origin. These innovative features laid the necessary groundwork for other planets to evolve and advance into new ideas for the crypto galaxy. Planet BTC's loyal and hardened community, having been through a civil war, welcomed the astronauts and provided them with basic knowledge about the galaxy.
